lead_paragraph: Benoit Cheyrou and Tosaint Ricketts scored in extra time as Toronto FC beat Montreal Impact 5-2 in the second leg of the Major League Soccer (MLS) Eastern Conference final on Wednesday, sealing a 7-5 aggregate victory.

headline.print_headline: Toronto to Play Seattle in MLS Final After Beating Impact
headline.main: Toronto to Play Seattle in MLS Final After Beating Impact
